    {
      "id": "recU8mSvvHgiyJ8gR",
      "createdTime": "2026-03-24T15:37:41.000Z",
      "fields": {
        "Date Added": "2026-03-24",
        "Project/Activity Summary - Story Content": "A short-term CSU faculty-led program in Germany & Austria provides opportunity for students to follow the exploration of European culture and history through immersion in the European equine industry. International focus on breeding, showing, managing and marketing of the horse is also an important part of this program. Students will have opportunities to visit several horse breeding and training facilities, major manufacturers of equipment, as well as observe training sessions, plus a variety of local cultural activities.\n",
